OL,3,CSmell of cannabis 'night in, night
OL,4,Cout' at troubled Parc Prison, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe smell of cannabis in the corridors
OL,8,Fof a Welsh prison was so prevalent
OL,9,Fthat everyone visiting "passed comment
OL,10,Fon it", an inquest has heard.
OL,12,FThe claims were read to the jury at an
OL,13,Finquest into the death of an inmate at
OL,14,FHMP Parc, in Bridgend.
OL,16,FRoss Appleby was found unresponsive in
OL,17,Fhis cell in January 2023 after taking
OL,18,Fsynthetic cannabis, or 'Spice.'
