OL,3,CSmell of cannabis 'night in, night
OL,4,Cout' at troubled Parc Prison, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FIn an inquest heard at Pontypridd
OL,8,FCoroners office on Tuesday, October 7,
OL,9,Fan e-mail from a prisoner officer at
OL,10,FParc to a senior manager was read to
OL,11,Fthe court.
OL,13,FThe e-mail, dated April 7th 2023,
OL,14,Freferred to an 'Accident Report' made
OL,15,Fby the officer, Michael Gardner, the
OL,16,Fprevious week.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
