OL,3,CSmell of cannabis 'night in, night
OL,4,Cout' at troubled Parc Prison, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FWriting to Gary Matthews, the Health
OL,8,Fand Safety, Environment and Fire
OL,9,FAdvisor at the prison, Mr Gardner said
OL,10,Fthat "nobody had followed up" his
OL,11,Freport from March 31st.
OL,13,FThe officer complained about "severe
OL,14,Fheadaches and lack of energy" while on
OL,15,Fduty, brought about, he said, by
OL,16,Fcannabis fumes on the prison's 'B'
OL,17,Fwing.
