OL,3,CSmell of cannabis 'night in, night
OL,4,Cout' at troubled Parc Prison, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"Night in, night out, I and others are
OL,8,Fexposed to this."
OL,10,FMr Gardner added that the issue had
OL,11,Fbecome a "bit of a joke" among some at
OL,12,Fthe prison.
OL,14,FDeb Lines, who was Head of Residence
OL,15,Fat Parc at the time of Mr Appleby's
OL,16,Fdeath, told the court she was
OL,17,F"disappointed" to hear Mr Gardner's
OL,18,Fclaims.
