OL,3,CSmell of cannabis 'night in, night
OL,4,Cout' at troubled Parc Prison, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"Of course it's concerning. I can't
OL,8,Frecall it being raised as a concern at
OL,9,Fthe time. But I'm not disputing that
OL,10,F(Mr Gardner's) experience was valid."
OL,12,FQuestioned by the coroner, Mr David
OL,13,FRegan, Ms Lines said that she'd expect
OL,14,Fissues like those reported by Mr
OL,15,FGardner to be brought to her attention.
OL,17,FBut she added that she couldn't find
OL,18,Fany record of the complaint.
