OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"Do you recognise the severity of the
OL,8,Fcomplaint Mr Gardner made at that
OL,9,Fstage?", Mr Regan asked.
OL,11,F"But you were not aware of it?"
OL,13,F"Nothing about a whole unit (being
OL,14,Faffected). I've searched all the areas
OL,15,Fwhere that could have been documented
OL,16,Fand unfortunately I couldn't find
OL,17,Fanything."
