OL,4,Cout' at troubled Parc Prison, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAsked about Mr Gardner's suggestion
OL,8,Fthat managers at Parc treated the
OL,9,Fsmell of cannabis in the prison as "a
OL,10,Fbit of a joke", Ms Lines said she'd be
OL,11,F"very disappointed " if that were the
OL,12,Fcase.
OL,14,F"I can only say that wouldn't have
OL,15,Fbeen the attitude of management. If
OL,16,Fthat's his perception I can't argue
OL,17,Fwith that.
OL,19,F"We take prevention very seriously.
OL,20,FIt's one of our biggest topics of
OL,21,Fconversation."
