OL,3,CSmell of cannabis 'night in, night
OL,4,Cout' at troubled Parc Prison, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"A piece of cannabis could make 30 or
OL,8,F40 joints. Spice can be put onto
OL,9,Fthousands of pages (of paper). It's
OL,10,Fcheap to make, easy to distribute and
OL,11,Fhard to detect.
OL,13,F"It's a constantly moving picture."
OL,15,FMs Lines agreed that Mr Appleby had
OL,16,Faccess to support and education around
OL,17,Fdrugs while at Parc, and that there
OL,18,Fwas nothing in prison risk assessments
OL,19,Fto say he was at risk.
