OL,3,CSmell of cannabis 'night in, night
OL,4,Cout' at troubled Parc Prison, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"We have a robust intelligence-
OL,8,Fgathering procedure to indicate where
OL,9,Fwe should be looking.
OL,11,F"There was nothing on our radar about
OL,12,FMr Appleby at that time."
OL,14,FThe witness was also asked about an
OL,15,Fincrease in reports of drug use at the
OL,16,Fprison in the months leading up to
OL,17,FRoss Appleby's death.
