OL,4,Cout' at troubled Parc Prison, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe court was previously told that
OL,8,Fthere had been an average of 219
OL,9,Fsubstance misuse observation reports
OL,10,Fper month between October 2022 and
OL,11,FApril 2023.
OL,13,FThe average for the 3 months
OL,14,Fbeforehand had been 116.
OL,16,FMs Lines said this could be due to a
OL,17,Fcombination of factors, including
OL,18,Fprison staff being "hyper-vigilant"
OL,19,Ffollowing a drugs death.
