OL,3,CSmell of cannabis 'night in, night
OL,4,Cout' at troubled Parc Prison, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F17 inmates are known to have died at
OL,8,FParc Prison since 2024, more than at
OL,9,Fany other UK prison. Five were
OL,10,Fbelieved to be drugs related.
OL,12,FAn unannounced inspection of HMP Parc
OL,13,Fin January found drugs were widely
OL,14,Favailable, with deliveries to cell
OL,15,Fwindows via drones.
OL,17,FAsked if the increase in reports in
OL,18,F2022/23 implied the prison was
OL,19,F"failing" to stop drugs coming in, Ms
OL,20,FLines said staff were working
OL,21,F"incredibly hard."
