OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"It's an incredibly difficult job."
OL,9,F"But we have a team which works
OL,10,Fincredibly hard to stop drugs coming
OL,11,Fin as no one wants to be in that
OL,12,Fposition."
OL,14,FThe inquest continues.
